items.title: Ted Cruz compares FCC Chair Carr to Mafia boss in Jimmy Kimmel warnings
items.description: Republican Sen. Ted Cruz of Texas sharply criticized Federal Communications Commission Chairman Brendan Carr over his comments related to Jimmy Kimmel...

items.title: Trump says 'I'm winning' after judge tosses his $15 billion NY Times lawsuit
items.description: Judge Steven Merryday noted that Trump's defamation lawsuit against The New York Times "consumes" 85 pages.

items.description: President Donald Trump and Chinese leader Xi Jinping held a much-anticipated call aimed at finalizing a deal to keep TikTok from going dark in the U.S...

items.title: Former Disney CEO Eisner backs Jimmy Kimmel, blasts FCC 'intimidation' of ABC
items.description: Disney and ABC have faced criticism for bowing to pressure from Federal Communications Commission Chairman Brendan Carr in benching Jimmy Kimmel.

items.title: ABC pulls Jimmy Kimmel show off air 'indefinitely' over Charlie Kirk comments
items.description: Jimmy Kimmel suggested that Tyler Robinson, the man accused of killing Charlie Kirk, was aligned with President Donald Trump's MAGA movement.
